{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no DP camp after that the first camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got to Munich, and then, and then the-- and it was really a lot of-- a, a lot of Jews came to Munich at the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when the DP camps were created by the UNNRA, I think, the United-- not the United Nations, United something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They created UNNRA, U-N-N-R-A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the DP camps were created.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, so in the [INAUDIBLE], we stayed in the, the Munich Museum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was bombed down, but we stayed in the Munich Museum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no art there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Big empty rooms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- in Austria, we stayed in [INAUDIBLE] hospital was half bombed-out, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in Munich, they, they really started resettling the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, they sent us to a small town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The name was [NON-ENGLISH], but we didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came back and said we'd rather go to the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to Fohrenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stayed in Fohrenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was really organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there was enough food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, there was shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Obviously, it was a barracks before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it, it was a big camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Fohrenwald was one of the biggest DP camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had Regensburg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the-- but Fohrenwald was a big, very well run DP camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And people were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A lot of people went to Israel before Israel became a state.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A lot of people want to Norway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, they're [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it had to be well over 2,000, 3,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was all survivors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All survivors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In camps, in hiding, all, all people leaving Russia, Poland, and trying to move west.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, all the way, even South America, anyplace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was moving someplace.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
